{"type": "article", "id": 12832, "title": "沙滩上的胶囊旅馆，不住帐篷时还有这些大脑洞住处供你选择", "description": "每间最多容纳两人入住。", "date": "2015-07-31T08:15:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4026, "name": "荷兰"}, {"id": 13728, "name": "胶囊"}, {"id": 13729, "name": "小型住宅"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 261, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134254L5TXFn4M97dvRDYo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t今年夏天，荷兰阿姆斯特丹的 centrumei land <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com:8080/art/urban-campsite-amsterdam-art-tents-07-27-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">主办了一个叫作 “urban campsite”（城市露营地）的活动</a>，这是一个公共展览，也是一个睡眠体验活动，共有十四位建筑师、设计师参与了项目，带来了他们的作品——一个个位于沙滩上的睡眠胶囊。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这十四个胶囊形态各异，富有想象力，有平屋顶的、带蹦床的、帐篷状的，还有能把头伸出球形舷窗的白色阁楼。<a href=\"http://www.urbancampsiteamsterdam.com\" target=\"_blank\">在活动主办方的官网上</a>，有着每间小屋子的详细信息和入住价格，它们均可以在 <span>airbnb </span>上预定。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134239L6HOfpCZGvFyNWQR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">这个作品的名字叫做 upside down you turn me，设计者是 Rob Sweere，居住者可以把头伸出四个舷窗。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134240OJH1mYVMhb2z7SdC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t内部的床长这样\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342403wVdftFzm6jbxvH0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这个作品则叫做 <span style=\"text-align:start;\">solid family ，作者是 Boomhuttenfest</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134241I9X37WG8CBbYM1hs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t建筑的内部结构，屋内空间并不大\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342415HJ2X6MfygTBVj87.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这是 <span style=\"text-align:start;\">val ross ，设计师是 MUD projects，看起来像是一个手雷</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134242GxkVsRYCJhLn0MFr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7359375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t打开盖子是这样子滴\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134242SwRYuse1NmGQ4LWb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t内部能容纳两个人\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342433465DLZCsTiJtzAy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">这个作品叫做 trampotent，设计者是 Vince Vijsma</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134243xI7V3smYcGukzn0U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t顶部是一张蹦床\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134244IXULDJvkSxAdEu1o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">这个叫做 ibc shrinkwrap ，设计者是 Refunc</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342445dbcoszTZPDy1IkF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t内部构造\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342441ujDb6pA04WSNTOm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">它叫 bedbug，创作者是 Franka te lintel hekkert 和 Ronnie Kommene，模仿的是臭虫的形状</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134245RAmuJvHLxS8UMGOB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t在作品的内部，有绿色的窗户和半金属的镶板\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134245TzJqRyWuwHNDg75h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">游客们坐在 superfine camp 旁边，它的设计者是 V</span>enividimultiplex\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134246Tlgp4D5k8nALfu0i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">universe 7 ，设计者是 </span><a href=\"http://doublebe.home.xs4all.nl/\" target=\"_blank\">robbert van der horst</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134246Ibxi9XcaDpQrBgVz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">universe 7 内部</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134247tkErRch8zlP5WQ7I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">carved from wood，设计者是 </span><a href=\"http://www.studioplots.nl/\" target=\"_blank\">studio plots</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134247SX3JvhbFtfYiDroR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t躺在内部\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342482ecVT0ABQnXzqPYa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.778125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">goahti ，设计者是 victor leurs</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134248EuVXNwFx2YdovRls.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t内部的光也是红色的\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134249AHW6GD1Erj3Vz0dy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.784375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">kite cabin ，设计师是 </span><a href=\"http://www.frankbloem.nl/\" target=\"_blank\">frank bloem</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134250X25lxfgV7WaqnIHk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.46875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t但这个白天会很热，晚上会很冷吧？\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342515RmDfYrBp4jndqLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\"> </span><a href=\"http://www.arjenboerstra.nl/\" target=\"_blank\">arjen boerstra</a> 设计的 attic\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021342520H7RnbixV92AF65o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t这是一个接待的“前台”\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134252edcOqa4pPhrbQMKw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:start;\">tribal toilet tower 的设计者是 </span><a href=\"http://www.ateliervanlieshout.com/\" target=\"_blank\">atelier van lie shout</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134253ywWMmibKktFU7Adj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tsuperfire camp\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.urbancampsiteamsterdam.com\" target=\"_blank\"><em>urban campsite</em></a> \r\n</p>\n\n"}